Task 1: Django ORM and API Endpoint

Objective: Test Django API development skills.

Prompt: Write a Django model for a Task object with the following fields:

id: AutoField (Primary Key)
title: CharField (max_length=255)
description: TextField (optional)
is_completed: BooleanField (default=False)
created_at: DateTimeField (auto_now_add=True)
Next, create an API endpoint /api/tasks/ to:

List all tasks.
Create a new task.
Include filtering functionality to return only completed tasks when the query parameter ?completed=true is passed.



